                            <comment id="13265083" author="daryn" created="Mon, 30 Apr 2012 18:27:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;During some pending yarn work, &lt;tt&gt;HttpServer&lt;/tt&gt; was returning -1 for the listening port on some of the tests.  I found that -1 is only returned if the socket is not bound.  This simplifies the logic of ensuring the port is bound.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
