                            <comment id="13265098" author="revans2" created="Mon, 30 Apr 2012 18:45:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The changes look good, and a lot simpler then they were before.  I like the new tests, and if everything passes I think it is OK.  Have you tested this on a cluster?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13265106" author="daryn" created="Mon, 30 Apr 2012 18:50:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I haven&apos;t brought this up on a full cluster, but yarn tests appear ok.  This is only about successfully binding, so there aren&apos;t host issues to worry about.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
